p.d: The Boat Show is a program dedicated to nautical lovers, boat owners, or dreamers, like ourselves. The Boat Show covers water tests, reports from international boat shows, visits to shipyards, boat maintenance and technology, everyday boat repair and maintenance tips, races, events, celebrities, cooking, safety, charters and ports. It is made with passion by a team of experts with more than 15 years of experience.
